Class Iso8601StringCalendarType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.type.impl.AbstractGenericBasicType<Calendar>
      • org.hibernate.ogm.type.impl.Iso8601StringCalendarType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, GridType, StringRepresentableType<Calendar>

    public class Iso8601StringCalendarType
extends AbstractGenericBasicType<Calendar>
    Type for persisting Calendar objects as String adhering to the ISO8601 format, either with or without time information but always with time zone information.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
